        <div class="content-body">
          <p>Great strategy starts with alignment. We work alongside your leadership team to build a shared understanding of where the business stands today, where it needs to go, and what it will take to get there. The result is a plan that every stakeholder can rally behind.</p>
          <p>Setting priorities is only half the battle. Our engagements help you distinguish the initiatives that will move the needle from the ones that simply consume resources. We pressure-test assumptions, model trade-offs, and ensure that the choices you make are grounded in evidence rather than intuition alone.</p>
          <p>A strategy without an execution roadmap is just a wish list. We translate high-level objectives into quarterly milestones, assign clear ownership, and build the review cadences your team needs to stay on track and adapt as conditions change.</p>
        </div>

